The paper discusses the Entity Disambiguation and Linking (EDL) task, which is a subfield of Information Retrieval (IR) and Natural Language Processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the need for high throughput and lightweight systems, which suggests a focus on database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) to achieve these goals.
